rComments: Extremely refined teacher who really knows his field. Excellent musician. Inspired and whimsical: not for the people who are looking for the usual boring way of teaching.I keep a great memory from his class!

Zank is a very knowledgeable professor and if it were not for his ego, condescending manner, and his inability to keep personal opinion out of his lectures, he would be a decent teacher. Also, it seems that at times he lacks enthusiasm and this hurts his lectures. Try to avoid if possible.
I didn't learn one thing from him or his lectures. I learned everything from reading the book and my discussion TA. The exams are alright, except the impossible listening parts.
